author_ssm: Thomas Beachdel, 2001. Collection materials added by Robert Feldman in January 2004 and Lisa Darms in July 2008.  Johan Kugelberg donation processed by Colin Wells in March 2009.
abstract_ssm: The collection consists of flyers and invitations relating to downtown galleries, performance spaces, and nightclubs. The bulk of the materials were collected by Mark Swartz, a downtown New York resident.
